Team Batman Proposal:
MineSweeper 

Project Description:
The ‘MineSweeper’ game is a classic computer game that challenges players to clear a grid of hidden mines without triggering any of them. This project aims to recreate the experience using the Java language, offering a graphical user interface for users to enjoy and test their strategic thinking and puzzle-solving skills.

Key Points/Target Features: 
1. Choose between Easy, Medium, Hard difficulties.
2. Randomized each time, not same level twice
3. Basic Minesweeper features, like “flagging” as well as the count of mines on the field.

FINAL VERSION: MineSweeperRenewed 5
